use package.json instead: https://github.com/amir20/phantomjs-node
modernizr to detect features https://modernizr.com/docs/#s2,  https://github.com/ariya/phantomjs/blob/master/examples/features.js
high-level convenient functionalities, check also projects such as CasperJS http://phantomjs.org/related-projects.html
integrate with mocha, chai, (installed babel-cli  chai  express  mocha  phantomjs  request  webdriverjs should)
	mocha usage
		1. "make test" usage : use Makefile to config mocha and run tests
		2. npm run mocha tests
		3. default mocha look for test/ folder for test cases, not tests/
Babel, ES6 (ES2015) http://info.meteor.com/blog/set-up-sublime-text-for-meteor-es6-es2015-and-jsx-syntax-and-linting (mostly for st3)
